My dotfiles and vim plugins managed with pathogen

To install:

1. Clone the folder into your home directory with this command: git clone git@github.com:Valve/dotfiles.git ~/.vim
2. Create symbolic links to files:
  ln -s ~/.vim/gitconfig ~/.gitconfig
  ln -s ~/.vim/hgrc ~/.hgrc
  ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
  ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
3. Fetch pathogen bundles from within your .vim directory:
  git submodule init
  git submodule update
